      code depending on whether or not the condition is true.
    - 'Write an else if statement after an if statement and before an else statement.
      Syntax goes like this:'
    - "if(condition1)\r\n{\r\n  //runs if condition1 is true\r\n}"
    - "else if(condition2)\r\n{\r\n  //runs if condition1 is false & condition2 is
