    npcPos: 76
    npcSprite: {fileID: -1018686373385036869, guid: 0060de204d35a494da2ce31a2aed8053, type: 3}
    lines:
    - 'So my conditions are "num < 20" and "num < 40" and I write the following statements:'
    - "if(num < 20)\r\n{\r\n  Bot.say(\"less than 20\");\r\n}"
    - "else if(num < 40)\r\n{\r\n  Bot.say(\"more than 20, less than 40\");\r\n}"
    - "else\r\n{\r\n  Bot.say(\"more than 40\");\r\n}"
    - If num is 10, num < 20 is true and G4wain says "less than 20".
    - 'If num is 30, num > 20 is false so it checks the second condition: num < 40
      is true, so G4wain says "more than 20, less than 40".'
    - And if num is 50 neither condition is true so, G4wain says "more than 40".
  - npcName: Morgan
